<s id="1999_1s_s741">1 - Oppalaččat </s>
<s id="1999_1s_s742">Sámediggi oaidná ahte vuollásaš fágaráđiid jahkedieđáhusain boahtá ovdan ahte lea dárbu ovttas bargat ja koordineret . </s>
