<s id="1999_1s_s2792">Artihkal 4 . </s>
<s id="1999_1s_s2793">Sámi parlamentáralaš ráđi bargoviidodahkii gullet buot áššit mat ráđi áddejumi mielde gusket dahje sáhttet guoskat sápmelaččaide sierra álbmogin . </s>
